<section class="music-section" id="music">
    <div class="music-text-container">
        <h2>Music in Mount Edgecombe</h2>
        <p>Mount Edgecombe is a vibrant community where music plays an integral role in shaping its culture. The diverse backgrounds of the people here bring together a variety of musical genres, each contributing to the unique atmosphere of the area. Some of the most prominent genres in the community include:</p>

        <div class="music-genres-container">
            <div class="music-genre-card">
                <h3>Traditional African Music</h3>
                <p>Rooted in the rhythms and sounds of the Zulu people, this genre is characterized by drumming, chanting, and dancing. It plays an essential role in cultural ceremonies and gatherings, fostering unity and a deep connection to the community's heritage.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="music-genre-card">
                <h3>Hindu Bhajans and Kirtans</h3>
                <p>In the Hindu community, devotional music in the form of bhajans and kirtans is an important part of religious practice. These songs are sung in praise of deities and are often accompanied by instruments like the tabla and harmonium. These musical traditions create a spiritually uplifting atmosphere during temple gatherings and festivals.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="music-genre-card">
                <h3>Western Music and Pop</h3>
                <p>European influence has brought Western music styles to Mount Edgecombe, with genres like pop, rock, and classical music being popular in social events and celebrations. Local bands and performers often play covers of international hits, blending global music trends with local flair.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="music-genre-card">
                <h3>Gospel Music</h3>
                <p>Christianity in Mount Edgecombe has fostered a strong tradition of gospel music, with choirs and church groups performing uplifting hymns and contemporary Christian music. Gospel events bring the community together for worship and celebration, with energetic performances that reflect faith and joy.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p>Music serves as a powerful tool for community bonding in Mount Edgecombe. Whether it’s through traditional beats, devotional songs, or modern genres, the diverse musical traditions enrich the cultural tapestry of the area and help bring people together across different backgrounds.</p>
    </div>
</section>
